---
layout: base.njk
title: Web Everything — Adapters
---

<section class="intro">
  <h1>Adapters</h1>
  <p>
    Adapters are <strong>format- and library-bridges</strong>. Rendering adapters let teams author in
    HTML, JSX, or template strings and compile to the same Web Everything primitives; syntax and library
    adapters bridge alternative authoring forms and incumbent libraries into the standard. Each adapter
    below links to its full specification.
  </p>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9em;">
    Adapters are owned by the <a href="/projects/webadapters/">Web Adapters</a> project — see it for the
    narrative grouping and rationale.
  </p>
</section>

{% for category in adapters %}
<section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
  <h2 id="{{ category.id }}" style="font-size: 1.1em;">{{ category.title }}</h2>
  {% if category.description %}<p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 0.25rem;">{{ category.description | safe }}</p>{% endif %}
  <div class="project-grid">
    {% for adapter in category.items %}
    <a href="/adapters/{{ adapter.id }}/"
       class="project-card"
       style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: block;">
      <div class="project-header" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
        <h3 class="project-title" style="margin: 0;">{{ adapter.name }}</h3>
        <span style="padding: 0.1rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 9999px; background: {% if adapter.status == 'implemented' %}#dcfce7{% elif adapter.status == 'draft' %}#dbeafe{% else %}#f1f5f9{% endif %}; color: {% if adapter.status == 'implemented' %}#166534{% elif adapter.status == 'draft' %}#1e40af{% else %}#475569{% endif %}; font-size: 0.75em; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap;">{{ adapter.status | title }}</span>
      </div>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9em;">{{ adapter.summary | safe }}</p>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endfor %}
